sequenceDiagram
    participant B as Browser
    participant S as Go Server
    participant T as Login Tracker
    participant DS as Firestore

    B->>S: POST /login (agreement + dob|postcode)
    S->>T: IsBlocked(agreement)?

    alt Locked out (5+ failures)
        T-->>S: blocked
        S-->>B: 302 /login-error
    else Not blocked
        T-->>S: ok
        S->>DS: FindByAgreementNumber
        DS-->>S: Agreement
        S->>DS: FindByCustomerID
        DS-->>S: Customer
        S->>S: Compare DOB (date only)
        S->>S: Compare postcode (normalised)

        alt Credentials match
            S->>T: RecordSuccess
            S->>S: Create session (AES-256-GCM)
            S-->>B: 302 /my-account + Set-Cookie __session
        else Mismatch
            S->>T: RecordFailure
            S-->>B: 302 /login-error
        end
    end
